17:T444,This is clearly a surgical instrument set for the Variabilis 2.4mm locking plate system. The 2.4mm plate size is standard for small fragment fixation in hand, wrist, and foot applications. The internal evidence is coherent and describes an instrument set with multi-angle plate drill sleeve specific to the Variabilis system. However, brand attribution is missing (no manufacturer confirmation beyond 'Meril'), and without external verification or catalog documentation, I cannot confirm: (1) the complete contents of the instrument set beyond the drill sleeve mentioned, (2) whether Variabilis is a Meril proprietary brand or licensed, (3) the exact anatomical indications claimed by the manufacturer. The 2.4mm dimension strongly suggests small bone/fragment applications. Classification enriched with probable anatomy scope based on standard orthopedic sizing conventions, but external verification needed for brand ownership, complete instrument list, and FDA/regulatory clearance scope. Recommended for review to confirm manufacturer brand ownership and complete instrument set contents.7:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"Variabilis 2.4mm Locking Plate System Instrument Set\",\"description\":\"Variabilis 2.4mm Locking Plate System Instrument Set including Multi-Angle Plate Drill Sleeve specific for Variabilis Plate.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"category\":\"Instrument Sets\",\"manufacturer\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateOffer\",\"offerCount\":\"1\",\"lowPrice\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"INR\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\"}}"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-24","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"flex mb-10 text-sm text-